{"tid":1405490,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"大家明天晏啲起身","createTime":"2019-08-04T09:57:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T15:16:37.000Z","uid":179167,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d040675e6943b5718f11a9aef730208b8a56f4a5","tid":1405490,"uid":179167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T09:57:08.000Z","msg":"之前0730玩地鐵叫無傷大雅<br />\n<br />\n但太早開始，真係會癱瘓香港<br />\n大家千祈唔好咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n0630左右開始處處開花，到到㩒掣，突然又見暈要職員幫手<br />\n忽然又快閃下呢條隧道、果條走廊，好似星期六玩紅隧咁，但玩埋東西隧、大老山<br />\n咁樣係唔啱，香港頂唔住嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n特別提醒駕駛人士注意安全<br />\n迴旋處又小心啲慢慢揸，撞左就麻煩<br />\n巴士司機又埋站頭先上落客<br />\n<br />\n尤其要重點講：港交所同青馬千祈唔好玩，好大鑊嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有車唔好揸出嚟塞主要通道，有人唔好玩快閃，唔好累死香港呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再奉勸大次：咁香港就會停擺，大家千祈唔好咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32fa8f2b23214a8abd3625c1c3366806ffa05065","tid":1405490,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:00:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推推推 推上去</span>"},{"pid":"caf91612f927d55466e3a30341fb615aa5753b21","tid":1405490,"uid":179167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:01:26.000Z","msg":"仲有龍和道、龍翔道、英皇道、皇后大道、彌敦道、屯門公路、環保大道，<br />\n大家唔好廿幾人一組咁玩，香港警力招架唔住，又搞衰經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"380d6cd22731bd1abc25cc4aab9301bbeb133367","tid":1405490,"uid":179167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:03:46.000Z","msg":"大家真係諗清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />經濟搞衰左大家冇運行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db48d85ffb0bab592db49d968d16daa7c99269bf","tid":1405490,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:35:57.000Z","msg":"香港仔陪隧道都好重要啊"},{"pid":"3fecee01cbcdb498786d9810790cbafe99e2fae0","tid":1405490,"uid":179167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db48d85ffb0bab592db49d968d16daa7c99269bf","tid":1405490,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:35:57.000Z","msg":"香港仔陪隧道都好重要啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:19:39.000Z","msg":"你提醒左大家，千祈唔好玩<br />\n唔好聽啲人講<br />\n有車出車、有人出人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d66eaf57ce4e5c22cb5bed966a48f6330810b983","tid":1405490,"uid":179167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:58:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbde5e8ecc9ca4dee5ecaa9437e4c9875a82959c","tid":1405490,"uid":179167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:30:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47487b41c4f9757a0b117993d30aaa06b60fa38b","tid":1405490,"uid":179167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:30:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f6461b605557936d62ec2651c3d7d5640fa1d7","tid":1405490,"uid":179167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:20:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faba4313d8cbe2f5b9fdc995c987d2f9d99d4eed","tid":1405490,"uid":179167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:20:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1da15ceb10b96e37421e608729cf4931ea3d327d","tid":1405490,"uid":179167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:20:25.000Z","m